This project — Intelligent Driver Monitoring System (DMS) — is developed
for educational and research purposes in the fields of:

  • Computer Vision
  • Machine Learning & Deep Learning
  • Real-time embedded AI systems

It is freely available for academic study, university coursework, personal
learning, and professional non-commercial research. Contributions, forks,
and derivative academic works are warmly welcomed.

If you use this project in academic work, a citation or acknowledgement is
appreciated but not required.
